fdd:adoption.p:
The following software libraries or applications for numerical computation can read or write Level 5 MAT-files:	Mathematica, see Wolfram Language; Maple;
Lumerical, see mat files;
MATLAB MAT-file Viewer;
GNU Octave, an open source package, see Simple File I/O;  	Math.NET Numerics, part of an open-source initiative.
